metadata.name: Genesis Mystery Egg
metadata.description:
The Mystery Egg Game

Welcome, the Mystery Egg Game is at your fingertips, but you'll have to be smart to get there.
In it you will find a world of puzzles and quests, you can take part in a huge treasure hunt that will bring you fame and fortune.

Traitors, allies, false leads and clues, be careful with everything you may find on your way.
The goal is simple, you have 12 quests to solve. The first one who finds all 12 passwords wins the Mystery Egg Game.

Everyone can try their luck but only the smartest will win.

Ready? The game starts now.

Follow your guide, Meggy Strey, oracle and protector of the Mystery Egg
